<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Submission Unsubmitted Notification</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset styles */
        body, h1, h2, p {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .header img {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .content {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .submission-details {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .submission-details p {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .action {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #c82333;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://dropovercl.s3.amazonaws.com/993b198a-3729-4081-89c1-3caede28ffd4/af2a0d39-b5b2-4354-87ba-fc829bc7f7aa/09869afa-1953-4a92-baea-9b4315eca3e7.png" alt="Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <%= marketingCoordinatorName %>,</p>
            <p>A student has <strong>unsubmitted</strong> their submission. Below are the details:</p>
            <div class="submission-details">
                <p><strong>Student Name:</strong> <%= studentName %></p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= studentEmail %></p>
                <p><strong>Date Unsubmitted:</strong> <%= submissionDate %></p>
            </div>
            <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please follow up with the student.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="action">
            <a href="<%= linkToViewSubmission %>" class="btn">View Student Profile</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 E Magazine System. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
